  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK787">
<l>aḻivi ṉavainīkki yāṟuyt taḻiviṉka</l>
<l>ṇallal uḻappatā naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(True) friendship turns aside from evil (ways) makes (him) walk in the (good) way, and, in case of loss if shares his sorrow (with him).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
